The Postmaster of Mafdet holds an open commission for a complete route survey of the Sands of Akh'enet. The ruins and desert approaches in the Akh'enet region lack current documentation in the harbor authority's reference files, creating navigation gaps for outbound expeditions and returning caravans alike. Survey every traversable section and return with a complete route record.
Your Akh'enet survey has been filed with Mafdet's harbor authority reference office. The postmaster has closed the commission and the route record has been incorporated into the outbound expedition documentation used by caravan operators departing the harbor.
